So <@U4F6H0FB9>, to answer your question, you can have
```
&lt;label&gt;
  &lt;input type="checkbox"&gt;
  Label text
&lt;/label&gt;
```

But you should still associate your label to your input. i.e.
```
&lt;label for="chk"&gt;
  &lt;input type="checkbox" id="chk"&gt;
  Label text
&lt;/label&gt;
